THINGS TO AVOID!!!!######
##Backend##
Don’t use absolute file paths (C:/Users/...)

Don’t forget methods=["POST"] on form routes

Don’t return plain strings when you should use render_template

Don’t store sensitive data in CSV

##HTML##
Don’t use <br><br><br> for spacing — use CSS margin

Don’t inline CSS everywhere

Don’t forget name="" attributes in forms

##CSS##
Don’t use fixed widths like width: 500px on everything

Don’t style IDs (#id) when classes (.class) are reusable

Don’t mix too many fonts or colours
